# --- NetBeans Specific ---
# Contains user-specific settings (like file paths on your machine)
**/nbproject/private/

# Build and distribution directories
**/build/
**/dist/
**/nbbuild/
**/nbdist/

# Configuration and Action files (often contain local paths)
**/nbactions.xml
**/nb-configuration.xml
**/.nb-gradle/

# --- General Java/Build Artifacts ---
# If you are using Maven
**/target/

# If you are using Gradle
**/.gradle/
**/build/

# Log files
*.log

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
